body:
This looks like the guilty commit:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/54cf1600b98127d5076def3c567cda1e087c1761

Basically, it seems like if you ever hit either of the 2 except clauses because your `eval_dict` throws the matching exceptions, you're going to then get an exception from `_write_summary_results`.
